HEADWORD: Turcism
<hw>Tur"cism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A mode of speech
peculiar to the Turks; a Turkish idiom or expression; also, in general,
a Turkish mode or custom. Same as <er>Turkism</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

